what_worked: Applied date_cte_isolate, dimension_cte_isolate, prefetch_fact_join: Materialized pre-filtered dimension (August 2002 dates) and store table in separate CTEs, then created a fact CTE that joins sales/returns with date constraints before the final aggregation.
why_it_worked: Pre-filtering date dimension into CTE reduces hash join probe table from 73K to ~365 rows; Pre-filtering all dimension tables into CTEs avoids repeated full-table scans; Pre-joining filtered dimensions with fact table before aggregation reduces join input
